Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:03.10,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,It’s because I’m weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.45,0:00:04.86,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Wait a second Lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:08.24,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You’re not a weird kid at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:18.82,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you're a kid with an active imagination, you're gonna have that kind of experience where you see human eyes in the patterns of a wooden ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:20.48,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,But that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:25.24,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Do you dislike being different from others?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:27.28,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I’m not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:28.25,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:30.92,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Lain is Lain because she is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:37.20,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You have a very strong imagination, and that’s a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:40.33,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,So don’t say that you're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:43.76,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I don’t think that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:46.05,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,But... the test...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:54.88,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, but... yeah, you’re troubled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:59.89,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I want to make sure you're not troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:03.86,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,In order to help you, I have to know more about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:07.14,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I don’t want you to do anything you dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:12.90,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I'll do anything I can to help you solve your problems. You're the only one who can truly understand yourself right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:16.58,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Nobody can understand Lain except Lain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.76,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Only you can solve your own problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:25.66,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,For me to be able to help you, I need your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:28.69,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:31.12,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Right now you don't need to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:40.82,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Since you and I are friends, if we keep talking, I’ll slowly start to understand more and more about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:51.16,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Then, sometimes I'll say "You might want to try this." and if you think "That sounds nice, okay.", let's try it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:56.86,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,So right now, it’d be best if you tell me all about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.76,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,You won’t tell anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:04.76,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Nope, it’ll be our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:07.73,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Not even my friends, or my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:13.09,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I promise. If I lie, one thousand needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:14.97,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,One thousand needles?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:17.86,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Don’t kids your age know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:26.52,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,When I was a kid, whenever we made a promise, we said, "If I break the promise, I will drink 1000 needles."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:27.77,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Wouldn’t that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:37.74,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,A lot!... Right! How many needles are in my stomach right now? Miss Iwakura? ...I was made to drink them 5 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.10,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,...five thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:44.61,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Wrong! Yesterday, since I went to the bathroom and flushed everything out, there’s zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.42,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Sensei, that's gross!...
